import { Home, Activity, ShoppingCart, Box, Menu, Circle, EyeOff, Folder, LifeBuoy, Shield } from 'react-feather'
export default [
  {
    id: 'tools',
    title: 'Tools',
    icon: <Box />,
    children: [
      {
        id: 'eCommerceDash',
        title: 'Network',
        icon: <Activity />,
        navLink: '/dashboard/ecommerce'
      },
      {
        id: 'analyticsDash',
        title: 'Development',
        icon: <Activity />,
        navLink: '/dashboard/analytics'
      },
      { id: 'explorer',
        title: 'Explorer',
        icon: <LifeBuoy />,
        externalLink: true,
        newTab: true,
        navLink: 'https://explorer.bitfari.com'
      },
      { id: 'projector',
        title: 'Projector',
        icon: <Folder />,
        externalLink: true,
        newTab: true,
        navLink: 'https://www.bitfari.com/projector/'
      },
      {
        id: 'audit',
        title: 'Audit',
        icon: <Folder />,
        externalLink: true,
        newTab: true,
        navLink: 'https://www.bitfari.com/audit/'
      },
     {
        id: 'screensaver',
        title: 'Screensaver',
        icon: <Folder />,
        externalLink: true,
        newTab: true,
        navLink: 'https://www.bitfari.com/display/'
      }
    ]
  }
]
